https://blog.logrocket.com/how-to-set-up-node-typescript-express/


npm i -D typescript @types/express @types/node

npx tsc --init --> generates tsconfig.json file
* unmute the outDir in the tsconfig.json file
* create a tsc file if some unkown error shows up in tsconfig.json file


ALTERNATIVELY you can use:
- tsc-node
- deno
etc...
